data.description: Check out one of the most unique homes in Fayette County!!  Massive 4 bedroom and 4 bath home with full basement sitting on nearly 2.5 acres with a creek going thru it and in Miami Trace school district!!Home features a gorgeous atrium that will wow you as you enter your new home. Then you will see the massive living room where you will be able to host all of the family for every holiday!!  Top of the line hvac system installed in 2021 that will make heating your new home very efficient. Now you can step out to one of the 2 elevated decks where you can sit and watch the kids fish and swim in the creek.  The basement walks out to a 36 x 12 screened porch where you can relax and enjoy your scenic back yard. So many more amenities but you just need to see this home for yourself!!
